OL,5, A New York City court has imposed      
OL,6, sweeping restrictions on British       
OL,7, billionaire Joe Lewis as he awaits     
OL,8, trial on insider trading charges.      
OL,10,FMr Lewis, 86, pleaded not guilty and   
OL,11,Fwas granted $300m (#230m) bail.        
OL,13,FBut the Manhattan judge required him to
OL,14,Fsurrender his passport and banned him  
OL,15,Ffrom using his superyacht.             
OL,17,FMr Lewis is not allowed to travel      
OL,18,Fabroad, including to the Bahamas       
OL,19,Foceanside resort he reportedly co-owns 
OL,20,Fwith Tiger Woods and Justin Timberlake.
